Yes, you heard it here first. Maina Kageni has been spotted receiving the brand new BMW X6 He is believed to be the the first owner of this car in East and Central Africa and we think he deserves it. Unfortunately, Maina doesn't like to show off so it will be difficult to see him in the streets with this car. Specifically, the BMW Maina Kageni owns is the BMW X6  xdrive 40i 2020 At the writing of this article, Maina could not be reached for comment. Here are some photos exclusively obtained by the-star.co.ke